{"id": 1449, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x饿了么】在“让过年轻松一点”这件事上，你有什么心得？", "description": "要想安稳过春节，说说你吃的堑长的智吧。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 1958, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170116173202hbM8OdsmaI1StG7V.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-19T03:00:30Z", "options": [{"id": 157184, "content": "没有春运，让我陪家人过个年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 884296}, {"id": 155649, "content": "在家看电视", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253159}, {"id": 156673, "content": "年夜饭差不多就行，别做太多了，不然新年前几天得天天吃剩饭剩菜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901085}, {"id": 155650, "content": "不要各种家庭聚会朋友聚会饭局等等等等 ……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 170829}, {"id": 155651, "content": "多穿衣服，不要被骂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729051}, {"id": 161283, "content": "少凑热闹，避开熊孩子，消停看书打游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 534750}, {"id": 155653, "content": "想去外面天天骑着小单车去吃不一样的好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737718}, {"id": 155654, "content": "年夜饭吃的是火锅…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875168}, {"id": 156166, "content": "不要走亲戚！少说话！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910846}, {"id": 155655, "content": "这原来还是广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 155656, "content": "准备点外币，比如日元，好发压岁钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909654}, {"id": 156680, "content": "假装没回国", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911890}, {"id": 157193, "content": "不出门不见人你们也别来我家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912964}, {"id": 155658, "content": "空军建军节", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 757263}, {"id": 156171, "content": "多喝酒。多看书，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477475}, {"id": 156939, "content": "玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347451}, {"id": 157195, "content": "不看不听不说不燥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912987}, {"id": 155660, "content": "晚去聚会 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903926}, {"id": 155661, "content": "陪爱的人一起过", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909678}, {"id": 156943, "content": "我家亲戚少?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912403}, {"id": 157199, "content": "爷爷生病了，，就在北方小年那天下午16:50突然发作，现在还在住院，祝爷爷早日康复", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912991}, {"id": 155666, "content": "滚得远远的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154}, {"id": 155667, "content": "时刻保持手机有电，在避免不了的聚会时，有个地方可以躲一躲。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826580}, {"id": 155668, "content": "#少说话 多做事#\n喝酒搓麻的都来者不拒 \n发钱唠嗑的都自动屏蔽 \n出门跑腿的都交给饿了么\n妥妥的欢天喜地中国年???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642260}, {"id": 155669, "content": "老老实实的，别搞得花枝招展，成为话题人物", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699652}, {"id": 155670, "content": "少吃点，不能让自己胖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900288}, {"id": 160023, "content": "同学聚会听一群没本事的人哭穷，变得没心没肺还自以为是。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781562}, {"id": 156440, "content": "别跟家里亲戚说自己回来了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898171}, {"id": 156954, "content": "挺好的～回来有段时间了～还得几天～可以了可以了，你忙～", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867107}, {"id": 155675, "content": "准备点越南盾，发压岁钱看着霸气！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 858291}, {"id": 155931, "content": "让过年过得轻松。。没有一点办法。。每天都很压抑。。虽然快要过年了。。陕西西安。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886398}, {"id": 155676, "content": "写几天计划并执行，培养一下自控力", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641419}, {"id": 156700, "content": "不想去逛无聊的花街 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583616}, {"id": 170269, "content": "出去玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943147}, {"id": 155678, "content": "潜心做菜给爸妈吃，或者和表哥表弟表姐表妹狐朋狗友外出约会", "image": "img/option/option/20170119143051gQ5svLKAtnUPpS0N.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654747}, {"id": 157470, "content": "可以像平时一样作息，饮食，保持节奏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913762}, {"id": 155681, "content": "在家多看点美剧、韩剧、英剧，尽量少到亲戚家走动……不然老妈喊你走完这家、永远还有下一家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642769}, {"id": 156449, "content": "陪家人的日子，无不轻松愉快！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911330}, {"id": 157474, "content": "对未来充满信心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913415}, {"id": 155684, "content": "真的不喜欢一群熊孩子来家里?，我的东西全被搞乱了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896457}, {"id": 196646, "content": "泡温泉去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014942}, {"id": 160295, "content": "春节期间出柜要谨慎", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920933}, {"id": 155688, "content": "看书（装X）", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840856}, {"id": 159272, "content": "长辈说什么赞同什么，即使反对也默默呆着就好，不用和他们太较真，等假期结束还是过自己的逍遥日子，至少脑子是自由的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916491}, {"id": 155689, "content": "不被问收入 不被逼婚 不被别人谈论自己的人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 873420}, {"id": 157993, "content": "少去电影院，过年吭钱的国产好多出来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914827}, {"id": 155690, "content": "少说话多吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898847}, {"id": 157996, "content": "多干活，多干活，眼里全是活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914803}, {"id": 155693, "content": "订饿了么（广告）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 174155}, {"id": 159021, "content": "微笑，点头，嗯", "image": "img/option/option/201701281239504dJ7IfQKLYojbZPe.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895651}]}